ZH: 1. 我们需要打下一个坚实的基石，才能建造一座高楼。
EN: We need to lay a solid foundation in order to build a skyscraper.
ZH: 2. 共同的价值观是我们合作的基石。
EN: Shared values are the cornerstone of our collaboration.
ZH: 3. 这个项目的成功基石是良好的沟通。
EN: Good communication is the cornerstone of the success of this project.
ZH: 4. 经济的稳定是国家繁荣的基石。
EN: Economic stability is the foundation of national prosperity.
ZH: 5. 在家庭中，互相尊重是家庭和谐的基石。
EN: Mutual respect is the cornerstone of family harmony.
ZH: 6. 沟通是建立良好领导力的基石之一。
EN: Communication is one of the foundations of good leadership.
ZH: 7. 科学研究是推动社会进步的基石。
EN: Scientific research is the cornerstone of social progress.
ZH: 8. 这个公司的发展取决于员工的敬业精神，这是公司文化的基石。
EN: The development of this company depends on the employees' dedication, which is the cornerstone of company culture.
ZH: 9. 教育被视为国家未来发展的基石。
EN: Education is seen as the cornerstone of a nation's future development.
ZH: 10. 和平与和谐是全球稳定的基石。
EN: Peace and harmony are the foundation of global stability.
ZH: 11. 文化遗产是国家文化的基石。
EN: Cultural heritage is the cornerstone of a nation's culture.
ZH: 12. 信任是建立成功合作关系的基石。
EN: Trust is the cornerstone of building successful partnerships.
ZH: 13. 尊重他人的观点是建立健康团队关系的基石。
EN: Respecting others' opinions is the foundation of building healthy team relationships.
ZH: 14. 领导者的诚信是组织正常运作的基石。
EN: The integrity of leaders is the cornerstone of the smooth operation of an organization.
ZH: 15. 知识是个人成功的基石。
EN: Knowledge is the foundation of individual success.
ZH: 16. 家庭支持是培养孩子自信心的基石。
EN: Family support is the cornerstone of nurturing children's self-confidence.
ZH: 17. 私有产权是市场经济的基石。
EN: Private property rights are the foundation of a market economy.
ZH: 18. 可持续发展的基石是环境保护。
EN: The cornerstone of sustainable development is environmental protection.
ZH: 19. 人权是民主社会的基石。
EN: Human rights are the foundation of a democratic society.
ZH: 20. 良好的领导是组织成功的基石。
EN: Good leadership is the cornerstone of organizational success.
